Resets the info component of the parsed query based on an arbitrary path-info string.

<code type="php">
$uri = Solar::factory('Solar_Uri');

$uri->import('http://example.com/index.php/something');
// now $uri->info is array('something');

// reset the path-info based on a new string
$uri->setInfoString('/more/path/info');

// now $uri->info is array('more', 'path', 'info');
</code>